title: ***Spacious Layouts With Panoramic Views - Open Weekends For Tour ***
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-Host Out of Town Guests Overnight in the Guest Suite', '-The Cyber Lounge Hosts a 24-hr, Self-Serve Coffee Bar, Pool Table and Computer Stations Making This a Great Place to Connect and Recharge', '-Package Concierge Offering 24-Hour Access to Packages', '-Brushed stainless kitchen faucet with pull-down sprayer', '-Walk in showers in select two and three bedroom apartments', '-The Patio Offerings a Peaceful Outdoor Lounging Space, Accented with Four Gas Grills and a Gas Fire Pit', '-Large, private balcony with panoramic views', '-Quality-crafted cabinetry with under cabinet lighting', '-Extra stuff?', 'Convenient Storage Lockers Available', '-Promenade Bike Trail and Bicycle Storage', '-The Cinema Offers Cozy Seating for Private Viewing Parties', '-Studio+ Highlighting Wellbeats!', 'Offering a Variety of On-Demand Exercise Programs', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
